name: opentsne
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "openTSNE" %}
{% set version = "0.6.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 92ea18afd4e34df8fb536c813c36533de892d96511f6683721003398b4fcf2e9

build:
  number: 1
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv
  skip: true  # [py<35]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
    - wheel
    - cython
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
  run:
    - numpy
    - python
    - scikit-learn >=0.20
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - openTSNE

about:
  home: https://github.com/pavlin-policar/openTSNE
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Extensible, parallel implementations of t-SNE
  doc_url: https://opentsne.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/pavlin-policar/openTSNE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pavlin-policar
